---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="AI Marketing & Social Media" description="AI-powered content pipelines, multi-channel publishing, email automation, and campaign analytics — built as a managed service or handed to your team.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section style="background:linear-gradient(160deg,#03142E 0%,#010A18 100%);padding:48px 24px 40px;text-align:center;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.1);">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">AI Marketing &amp; Social Media</div>
    <h1 style="font-family:var(--font-head);font-weight:700;font-size:clamp(22px,6vw,36px);letter-spacing:-0.01em;color:var(--silver);margin-bottom:10px;">Content at Scale.<br><em style="font-style:normal;color:var(--gold);">Consistency by Design.</em></h1>
    <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--silver-dim);line-height:1.6;max-width:460px;margin:0 auto 28px;">We build AI-powered marketing systems — content pipelines, social media management, email automation — that publish consistently without requiring a full marketing team.</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary" style="display:inline-block;min-width:220px;">Book a Discovery Call</a>
  </section>

  <!-- Problem -->
  <section style="padding:40px 24px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.08);max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">The Problem</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Marketing stalls when consistency is hard</h2>
    <p style="font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;color:var(--silver-dim);margin-bottom:16px;">Most companies publish when someone has time, which means sporadically. Algorithms punish inconsistency. Audiences don't develop. The content investment never compounds.</p>
    <p style="font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;color:var(--silver-dim);">The fix isn't hiring a bigger content team. It's building a system that produces and publishes on a reliable cadence — regardless of how busy the week gets. That's what AI-powered content infrastructure delivers.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- What we build -->
  <section style="padding:40px 24px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.08);max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">What We Build</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Four components of a working content engine</h2>

    <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.12);border-radius:6px;padding:20px;margin-bottom:12px;">
      <div style="font-family:var(--font-head);font-weight:600;font-size:15px;color:var(--silver);margin-bottom:6px;">Content Pipeline</div>
      <p style="font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--silver-dim);margin-bottom:10px;">Daily research sweep → strategy → writing → brand review → scheduled publishing. The entire production cycle runs automatically overnight. Your team wakes up to a full content package ready to review and approve.</p>
      <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--silver-muted);letter-spacing:0.05em;text-transform:uppercase;"><strong style="color:var(--gold);">Output:</strong> Blog · LinkedIn · X · Instagram · Telegram — daily</div>
    </div>

    <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.12);border-radius:6px;padding:20px;margin-bottom:12px;">
      <div style="font-family:var(--font-head);font-weight:600;font-size:15px;color:var(--silver);margin-bottom:6px;">Social Media Management</div>
      <p style="font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--silver-dim);margin-bottom:10px;">Multi-channel publishing with engagement monitoring, reply drafts, and warm prospect identification. Runs across LinkedIn, X, Instagram, and Telegram with platform-specific formatting and timing.</p>
      <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--silver-muted);letter-spacing:0.05em;text-transform:uppercase;"><strong style="color:var(--gold);">Output:</strong> 20–40 posts/week across 4 platforms, consistent brand voice</div>
    </div>

    <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.12);border-radius:6px;padding:20px;margin-bottom:12px;">
      <div style="font-family:var(--font-head);font-weight:600;font-size:15px;color:var(--silver);margin-bottom:6px;">Email Automation</div>
      <p style="font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--silver-dim);margin-bottom:10px;">Lead nurture sequences, re-engagement flows, and newsletter pipelines — written to brand voice, triggered by behavior, and optimized by open and click data.</p>
      <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--silver-muted);letter-spacing:0.05em;text-transform:uppercase;"><strong style="color:var(--gold);">Output:</strong> Automated sequences + monthly broadcast + list hygiene</div>
    </div>

    <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.12);border-radius:6px;padding:20px;">
      <div style="font-family:var(--font-head);font-weight:600;font-size:15px;color:var(--silver);margin-bottom:6px;">Campaign Analytics</div>
      <p style="font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--silver-dim);margin-bottom:10px;">Weekly performance dashboards: what's working, what isn't, and what to adjust. We surface the signal and make the changes — you don't need to read reports, you need outcomes.</p>
      <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--silver-muted);letter-spacing:0.05em;text-transform:uppercase;"><strong style="color:var(--gold);">Output:</strong> Weekly summary + monthly strategic review</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Formats -->
  <section style="padding:40px 24px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.08);max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">How We Work</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Managed service or handoff</h2>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <div style="flex:1;min-width:240px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.12);border-radius:6px;padding:20px;">
        <div style="font-family:var(--font-head);font-weight:600;font-size:14px;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:8px;">Managed Service</div>
        <p style="font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--silver-dim);">We operate the content engine for you. Monthly retainer. You approve, we publish. Suitable for companies that want results without building internal capability.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="flex:1;min-width:240px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.12);border-radius:6px;padding:20px;">
        <div style="font-family:var(--font-head);font-weight:600;font-size:14px;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:8px;">Build &amp; Handoff</div>
        <p style="font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--silver-dim);">We build the system, train your team, and hand over the keys. Fixed project scope. Suitable for companies that want the infrastructure internally operated.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(215,161,61,0.08) 0%,rgba(3,20,46,0.6) 100%);border-top:1px solid rgba(215,161,61,0.15);padding:40px 24px;text-align:center;">
    <div style="max-width:480px;margin:0 auto;">
      <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-head);font-weight:700;font-size:20px;color:var(--silver);margin-bottom:8px;line-height:1.3;">See what consistent publishing looks like</h2>
      <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--silver-dim);margin-bottom:24px;">A paid strategy call is 60 minutes with Hesam, recorded, with a one-page action memo. €149, credited toward bigger work if you start within 14 days.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary" style="display:inline-block;min-width:220px;">Book a Discovery Call</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
